      "date": "2013-03-05 05:17:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d242c31e-854f-11e2-926e-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  2 tests failed: replay-ost-single, sanity.",
